      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    £3 billion affordable housing guarantee scheme to be operated by Ara Venn
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Investment management firm ARA Venn to deliver £3 billion scheme that will provide cost-effective long-term loans to registered providers of affordable homes.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 16 October 2020
    <br></br>Last updated 16 October 2020
      — <a href="#history" class="app-c-published-dates__history-link govuk-link">see all updates</a>
</div>

